message: "If you use dexta-intelligence in your research, please cite it."
title: "dexta-intelligence"
abstract: >-
  A self-hosted agentic harness for Type 1 diabetes data that turns CGM,
  insulin, pump, and wearable history into traceable findings, with
  deterministic analytics, statistical rigor, a numeric-faithfulness guard,
  and a no-dosing treatment gate.
type: software
